#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:5
msgid "General"
msgstr "Umum"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:8
msgid ""
"All TibiaME rules are valid on this fansite. Please check FAQ section on "
"tibiame.com."
msgstr ""
"Semua peraturan TibiaME adalah sah di laman peminat ini. Sila semak bahagian "
"FAQ di tibiame.com."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:11
msgid "Accounts"
msgstr "Akaun"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:13
msgid "You are only allowed to use your real character nickname and gameworld."
msgstr ""
"Anda hanya dibenarkan untuk menggunakan nama samaran karakter sebenar dan "
"dunia permainan anda."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:14
msgid "You are not allowed to share your account data (password) publicly."
msgstr ""
"Anda tidak dibenarkan untuk berkongsi data akaun (kata laluan) anda secara "
"terbuka."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:17
msgid "Highscores"
msgstr "Skor Tertinggi"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:19
msgid "Listed characters"
msgstr "Karakter yang disenaraikan"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:22
msgid ""
"Top 100 wizards and top 100 warriors by total experience from each game "
"world are listed."
msgstr ""
"100 ahli sihir terbaik dan 100 pahlawan terbaik mengikut jumlah pengalaman "
"dari setiap dunia permainan adalah disenaraikan."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:23
msgid "Characters with PvP rank 100 or higher are listed."
msgstr ""
"Karakter dengan kedudukan PvP 100 atau lebih tinggi adalah disenaraikan."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:25
msgid ""
"Top 100 wizards and top 100 warriors by achievement points from each game "
"world are listed."
msgstr ""
"100 ahli sihir terbaik dan 100 pahlawan terbaik mengikut mata pencapaian "
"dari setiap dunia permainan adalah disenaraikan."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:26
msgid "Other characters are not listed and we cannot add them at this time."
msgstr ""
"Karakter lain tidak disenaraikan dan kami tidak dapat menambah mereka pada "
"masa ini."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:29
msgid "Data reliability"
msgstr "Kebolehpercayaan data"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:31
msgid "Highscores are updated daily at 00:10 UTC."
msgstr "Skor tertinggi dikemas kini setiap hari pada jam 00:10 UTC."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:33
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Highscores data are provided by tibiame.com and Tibia-ME.net is not "
#| "responsible for its reliability."
msgid ""
"Highscores data are provided by tibiame.com and we are not responsible for "
"its reliability."
msgstr ""
"Data skor tertinggi disediakan oleh tibiame.com dan Tibia-ME.net tidak "
"bertanggungjawab atas kebolehpercayaannya."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:35
msgid ""
"Worlds' statistics as well as Top Hunters data are only based on characters "
"that are listed on this website (see 3.1.)."
msgstr ""
"Statistik dunia serta data Pemburu Terbaik adalah hanya berdasarkan karakter "
"yang disenaraikan di laman web ini (lihat 3.1.)."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:40
msgid "Screenshots"
msgstr "Tangkapan Skrin"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:42
msgid "Only TibiaME screenshots are allowed at Screenshots section."
msgstr ""
"Hanya tangkapan skrin TibiaME yang dibenarkan di bahagian Tangkapan Skrin."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:43
msgid "Artworks are not allowed."
msgstr "Hasil seni adalah tidak dibenarkan."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:45
msgid ""
"Screenshots should not contain any non-game areas, e.g. computer desktop and "
"emulator window."
msgstr ""
"Tangkapan skrin tidak boleh mengandungi sebarang kawasan bukan permainan, "
"contohnya desktop komputer dan tetingkap emulator."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:48
msgid "Artworks"
msgstr "Hasil Seni"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:50
msgid "Artworks should be related to TibiaME."
msgstr "Hasil seni mestilah berkaitan dengan TibiaME."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:51
msgid "You are only allowed to upload your own artworks."
msgstr "Anda hanya dibenarkan untuk memuat naik hasil seni anda sendiri."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:54
msgid "Privacy"
msgstr "Privasi"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:56
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Tibia-ME.net never shares your hidden data (e.g. email, birth date) with "
#| "anyone."
msgid "We never share your hidden data (e.g. email, birth date) with anyone."
msgstr ""
"Tibia-ME.net tidak pernah berkongsi data tersembunyi anda (contohnya e-mel, "
"tarikh lahir) dengan sesiapa pun."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:58
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Your passwords are encrypted and cannot be viewed by anyone, including "
#| "Tibia-ME.net staff."
msgid ""
"Your passwords are encrypted and cannot be viewed by anyone, including our "
"staff."
msgstr ""
"Kata laluan anda adalah disulitkan dan tidak boleh dilihat oleh sesiapa pun, "
"termasuk kakitangan Tibia-ME.net."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:60
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Tibia-ME.net Admin may use your data to contact you (e.g. email, "
#| "including hidden data)."
msgid ""
"We may use your data to contact you (e.g. email, including hidden data)."
msgstr ""
"Admin Tibia-ME.net boleh menggunakan data anda untuk menghubungi anda "
"(contohnya e-mel, termasuk data tersembunyi)."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:63
msgid "Copyrights"
msgstr "Hak Cipta"

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:66
msgid ""
"TibiaME is a trademark of CipSoft GmbH, tibiame.com is the only official "
"TibiaME website."
msgstr ""
"TibiaME adalah tanda dagangan CipSoft GmbH, tibiame.com adalah satu-satunya "
"laman web rasmi TibiaME."

#: resources/views/agreement.blade.php:68
msgid ""
"Any icons provided by CipSoft are copyrighted by CipSoft. You may use any "
"TibiaME icons from this website."
msgstr ""
"Mana-mana ikon yang disediakan oleh CipSoft adalah hak cipta CipSoft. Anda "
"boleh menggunakan mana-mana ikon TibiaME daripada laman web ini."

